metadata.name: YOSHIROTTEN - SUN
metadata.description:
SUN

YOSHIROTTEN IS A TOKYO BASED ARTIST WHOSE WORK MOVES BETWEEN SEVERAL DIFFERENT REALMS: THE OPEN EDITION SUN HAS BEEN CREATED TO LAUNCH THE SERIES, ENTITLED SUN, WHICH CONSISTS OF 365 IMAGES OF THE SILVERY SUN. THE IMAGES ARE NOT AUTOMATICALLY GENERATED, BUT ARE PAINTED BY HAND USING DIGITAL TOOLS.
